{%- comment -%}
Critical paint styles for victory-band templates (vctry-landing, etc.).
Prevents white flash and breadcrumb flicker before alternate header/footer render.
{%- endcomment -%}
<style id="victory-band-critical">
html,
body.victory-band {
    background-color: #000;
    color: #fff;
}
body.victory-band .breadcrumb {
    display: none !important;
}
body.victory-band #app {
    background-color: #000;
}

</style>
